         <div type="commentary">
            <head>Commentary</head>
            <p>For a description of this church, which seems to have been built in the mid-VI
               century, see J.B. Ward Perkins and R.G. Goodchild, 'The Christian Antiquities of
               Tripolitania', <title level="j">Archaeologia</title>, xcv (1953) 29 ff. The type of tomb concerned here is the
               second and later group distinguished by these authors.</p>
         </div>
